verbose_text: Originally, the Fd-TRX system and TRXf1 were assigned to activate fructose-1,6-bisphosphatase (FBPase), seduheptulose-1,7-bisphosphatase (SBPase), glyceraldehyde-3-phosphate dehydrogenase (GAPDH), and phosphoribulokinase (PRK) in the CBB cycle [XREF_BIBR, XREF_BIBR, XREF_BIBR] as well as the gamma-subunit of ATP synthase [XREF_BIBR, XREF_BIBR].
